uk.co.strangeskies.reflection

Class TypeVariableCapture

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.co.strangeskies.reflection.TypeVariableCapture
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.reflect.AnnotatedElement, java.lang.reflect.Type, java.lang.reflect.TypeVariable<java.lang.reflect.GenericDeclaration>

    public class TypeVariableCapture
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.reflect.TypeVariable<java.lang.reflect.GenericDeclaration>
    A representation of an unknown instantiation of a type variable or inference variable which is known to satisfy a certain set of upper and lower bonds.
